      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh i didnt know about that... honestly i'm just panicking because his forehead is so hot. is there like a specific way i should dose the ibuprofen or something? i dont have the kids version in the house right now, just the adult stuff. can i just use the regular ones but maybe smaller doses?",
