      "content": "he's about 30kg so i think i can figure the math out. but i'm really worried about giving him adult meds, i feel like it's too risky. if i just give him half a pill of the adult ibuprofen, would that be safe enough to just get him through the night until the morning? i really don't want to take him to the a&e at this hour if it's not strictly necessary.",
